  • Constructor Details

    • Catch

      public Catch(long rowid, String flyType, int flySize, Catch.Water waterConditions, Catch.Weather weatherConditions, com.tylerspaeth.Catch.Location location)
      This method constructs a Catch object without being given a timeOfCatch. In this case, the date and time are set to null.
      Parameters:
      rowid - the rowid number in the database
      flyType - the type of fly that was used
      flySize - the size of fly that was used
      waterConditions - what the water conditions were when the fish was caught
      weatherConditions - what the weather conditions were when the fish was caught
      location - what type of water the fish was caught in

    • Catch

      This method constructs a Catch object.
      Parameters:
      rowid - the rowid number in the database
      flyType - the type of fly that was used
      flySize - the size of fly that was used
      waterConditions - what the water conditions were when the fish was caught
      weatherConditions - what the weather conditions were when the fish was caught
      location - what type of water the fish was caught in
      timeOfCatch - the date and time in which the fish was caught
